            "influenced"
          ],
          "translations": {
            "zh-TW": "新的稅制影響了許多小企業主，使他們延後投資。"
          }
        },
        {
          "en": "By influencing public opinion through social media, the brand quickly doubled its market share.",
          "highlight": [
            "influencing"
          ],
          "translations": {
            "zh-TW": "透過社群媒體影響輿論，這個品牌很快就把市占率翻了一倍。"
          }
        }
      ],
      "synonyms": [
        "affect",
        "impact",
        "shape"
      ],
      "antonyms": [
        "ignore",
        "neglect"
      ],
      "phrases": [
        "under the influence",
        "influence on",
        "strong influence",
        "influence decision"
      ]
    },
